Additionally, the paper discusses enhancing scientific workflows, which suggests that it may belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. The paper also discusses using the system to generate and expand models, which suggests that it may belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses using the system to enhance scientific workflows in a working case study, which suggests that it may also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
